posits, of which $151.5 billion were =E2=80=9Cestimated uninsured deposits =
in U.S. offices that exceed the FDIC insurance limit=E2=80=9D and $13.9 bil=
lion were foreign deposits =E2=80=9Cnot subject to any U.S. federal or stat=
e deposit insurance regime.=E2=80=9D


  [8] For a while Signature Bank was in the same boat, but then  it got sol=
d.


