om-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> ge=
ntly suggested</a> that US banks should be careful about crypto deposits, a=
nd=C2=A0all of the crypto-friendly US banks <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bl=
oombergbusiness.com/click/30973470.267437/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvb=
S9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDMtMDIvc2lsdmVyZ2F0ZS1oYWQtYS1jcnlwdG8tYmFu=
