rder-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">  dropped a hint</a> tha=
t Coinbase Global Inc., the largest US crypto exchange, might be illegal, b=
ecause it lists a variety of crypto tokens and the SEC thinks that almost a=
ll of them (not Bitcoin) are securities. Various bits of the crypto financi=
